Package: bristolthesis
Type: Package
Title: An updated thesisdown package for the University of Bristol
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Matthew", "Lee", email = "matthew.lee@bristol.ac.uk", role = "cre")
Maintainer: Matthew Lee <matthew.lee@bristol.ac.uk>
Description: 
    bristolthesis is an adaptation of thesisdown to produce a thesis that can be used at the University of Bristol.
    The thesisdown package uses bookdown and LaTeX and word templates from Reed College. We use this as a basis for bristolthesis.        
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.2.0),
    devtools,
    dplyr,
    ggplot2,
    bookdown,
    knitr,
    kableExtra,
    flextable
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1
